her glancing at me one extra time

591
00:22:19,599 --> 00:22:20,839
spending a little more time with me

592
00:22:22,759 --> 00:22:24,039
saying a few more words to me

593
00:22:25,180 --> 00:22:26,279
and my heart...

594
00:22:26,460 --> 00:22:27,500
just feels warm

595
00:22:28,440 --> 00:22:29,779
I can be happy all night

596
00:22:30,440 --> 00:22:31,720
and savor it for days

597
00:22:34,319 --> 00:22:35,319
That's all there is to it

598
00:22:35,660 --> 00:22:36,759
The sunset is glowing

599
00:22:44,200 --> 00:22:45,599
Boss Li's bean

600
00:22:45,799 --> 00:22:49,220
The first character is already very clear.

601
00:22:49,279 --> 00:22:50,319
It's the word "Love".

602
00:22:52,599 --> 00:22:53,799
It seems...

603
00:22:54,200 --> 00:22:55,900
there are five words in total.

604
00:22:56,019 --> 00:22:57,920
It must be "Love is worth more."

605
00:22:58,000 --> 00:22:59,140
It shows that I am a...

606
00:22:59,220 --> 00:23:00,420
person who values love highly,

607
00:23:00,420 --> 00:23:01,539
someone worth trusting.

608
00:23:02,480 --> 00:23:04,220
This last character...

609
00:23:04,380 --> 00:23:05,200
is "Win".

610
00:23:05,720 --> 00:23:07,660
"No pain, no gain."

611
00:23:08,220 --> 00:23:08,759
Hurry and check...

612
00:23:08,759 --> 00:23:09,519
what bean I have.

613
00:23:10,279 --> 00:23:11,660
Four words in total.

614
00:23:11,839 --> 00:23:13,960
The first word is "Intertwined".

615
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:16,099
I made it out.

616
00:23:16,380 --> 00:23:17,799
"Intertwined branches, shared home."

617
00:23:18,599 --> 00:23:19,380
What does that mean?

618
00:23:19,380 --> 00:23:20,880
It's "Intertwined branches, shared tomb."

619
00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:21,539
It describes...

620
00:23:21,619 --> 00:23:22,880
steadfast love.

621
00:23:23,740 --> 00:23:25,839
That means my love is very steadfast.

622
00:23:29,259 --> 00:23:30,220
Thank you.

623
00:23:30,220 --> 00:23:31,960
Thank you, children.

624
00:23:32,359 --> 00:23:33,059
Of course,

625
00:23:33,440 --> 00:23:35,119
thank you two as well.

626
00:23:35,819 --> 00:23:37,359
For taking care of my Magic Bean.

627
00:23:37,519 --> 00:23:38,460
Ms. Liu,

628
00:23:38,579 --> 00:23:40,259
between these two pots of Magic Beans,

629
00:23:40,519 --> 00:23:42,180
which one do you prefer?

630
00:23:42,940 --> 00:23:43,599
Which pot do you like?

631
00:23:43,599 --> 00:23:44,900
Say it, don't be shy.

632
00:23:45,019 --> 00:23:46,259
Don't be shy.

633
00:23:48,380 --> 00:23:49,279
I like them both.

634
00:23:49,660 --> 00:23:50,359
Like them both?

635
00:23:50,779 --> 00:23:53,200
Because you are all my forever...

636
00:23:53,420 --> 00:23:54,559
best friends.
